  "text": [
    "As I am Catholic",
    "I have never played.",
    "* * *",
    "I've had",
    "thirty-six lovers",
    "plus tax.",
    "* * *",
    "I am the most chaste woman",
    "in Italian literature.",
    "* * *",
    "I am completely",
    "asexual",
    "not counting errors",
    "and omissions.",
    "* * *",
    "Mount Sinai",
    "is sometimes confused",
    "with the Mons Veneris.",
    "* * *",
    "No one can know",
    "what is",
    "between me and God."
  ],
  "title": "Aphorisms and Spells",
  "year": ""
}